Adjoyning to this Country lyeth Boena, and Bamff a small Sheriffdom;
also Ajuza, a little Territory of no great note.
Marr.

In this track are three Promontories, to wit, Urdehead,
of old Berubium;
Dunsby or Dunscanby, of old Virvedrum; and Howbum, of old Orcas.
